    website are based on current industry knowledge at the time of writing. The technology landscape
    evolves rapidly, and eLan Technology does not guarantee that any specific technology, platform,
    or tool will remain suitable, supported, or optimal for any given purpose indefinitely.
  </p>

  <h2>Pricing</h2>
  <p>
    Any pricing, cost estimates, or package details displayed on this website are indicative only
    and are subject to change without notice. All final pricing is confirmed in a written project
    proposal or service agreement issued directly to the client. Indicative prices do not constitute
    a binding offer.
  </p>

  <h2>Professional Advice</h2>
  <p>
    Nothing on this website constitutes legal, financial, accounting, tax, or other professional
    advice. For matters requiring professional expertise in these areas, you should consult a
    qualified and appropriately licenced professional in your jurisdiction.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions about this disclaimer or the information on our website, please
    contact us at:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Email: <a href="mailto:info@elan-tech.net">info@elan-tech.net</a></li>
    <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+918788834630">+91 8788834630</a></li>
    <li>
      Address: eLan Technology, Basement Floor, PTG IT Park, Plot No. 21, IT Park Rd,
      Gayatri Nagar, Nagpur, Maharashtra 440022, India
    </li>
  </ul>
</LegalLayout>
